# Frontend Instructions

- Consider user-visible behavior, loading states, error states, and accessibility together.
- Do not over-mix UI rendering, business logic, and API normalization in one file.
- Keep components small and move shared state or async orchestration into clearer layers.
- When UI behavior changes, update the related tests or docs in the same change.
- Follow the shared rules in `AGENTS.md` and `CLAUDE.md`.
